{"tid":1104871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家睇車，關sir未撚解釋件事就想洗白有冇咁著數","createTime":"2019-04-13T12:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T04:03:15.000Z","uid":57911,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb573d9d1871751ad4e9666142b9ad1f65783084","tid":1104871,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1098389/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1098389/page/1</a><br />\n關sir自己開嘅還我何俊謙一個清白<br />\n但全post並未有正面回應事件<br />\n有三分一個post係離題屌仇狗同奧雲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1104364/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1104364/page/1</a><br />\n無人格的毒男：本土派的不義, 關愛座hunter已經親自證明<br />\n<br />\n重點係關sir件事過咗成個月都未正面回應過件事<br />\n而佢連佢自己學位嘅嘢都冇撚出嚟交代過<br />\n咁就想洗白有冇咁著數"},{"pid":"dca04c72400b81b3b3e58d5f870d9cbe849975bc","tid":1104871,"uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:36:24.000Z","msg":"除咗上d100仲有做過啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd191b01b432463d35ebcffd91f884dfae00ed1","tid":1104871,"uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:37:17.000Z","msg":"學位跟進成點冇人知<br />\n關sir面對指控就只會潛<br />\n學位都不重要了"},{"pid":"4e71b9edf2050576679586abf268c8ebe0f9b65f","tid":1104871,"uid":123456,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關大關惡關正確<br />\npoly學生會=五毛=迫害關蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"13f677ebf32f86e994e00f1ba39ed90c0910dc05","tid":1104871,"uid":68876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"撳偏咗變負皮，sor~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmo